      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有个独立的DATAS服务，我标注为PARTICIPANTS DATA。整个流程是：CALLER打到FLOW，FLOW立刻启动ASYNC WORKFLOW，然后FLOW去DATAS轮询状态，而不是干等。",
      "elements_involved": [
